parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the power steering pump fails
the vehicle is hard to steer
the steering wheel becomes stiff
the power steering assist fails
the vehicle experiences intermittent power steering failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering pump can cause the power steering system to fail, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The power steering pump fails
the power steering pump stops functioning intermittently
the power steering pump continues to operate after the vehicle is turned off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the manufacturer to include certain vehicles in the recall or to provide adequate warranty coverage can lead to owners being left with costly repairs and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle is not included in the recall
the manufacturer refuses to repair the vehicle under warranty
the dealer is unable to diagnose or repair the issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Faulty Passenger Seat Occupancy Mat Sensor
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty sensor can cause the passenger airbag to be disabled, which can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light illuminates
the passenger airbag is disabled
the sensor mat fails to detect the presence of a passenger
and the airbag warning light turns on and off randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag light illumination can indicate a faulty airbag system, which can lead to serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light illuminates
the airbag warning light turns on and off randomly
and the passenger airbag is disabled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delayed or unavailable recall repairs can lead to continued use of a vehicle with a faulty airbag system, which can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The recall repair is delayed or unavailable
the part needed for the repair is unavailable
and the manufacturer exceeds a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair.
